channel.title: MoparScape Server Status Problem
channel.description: Yea so I posted my server up on the MoparScape Server Status Forums and it has been atleast 6 hours or more and it still has not been posted. My server is online but I guess there is a problem with the Status Checker. If any type of staff personal could contact me by any chance on what the problem is that would be GREAT! thanks. If you need the supposed to be status page it is SUPPOSED to be, http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=deltascape.servegame.com . Please can I get some help. Lol :confused: :/
